data.description: Welcome to your dream colonial-style home, a picturesque retreat that combines classic charm with modern amenities. Nestled in the welcoming community of Oregon, this residence offers an expansive and thoughtfully designed layout. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting ambiance of the spacious living rm featuring new flooring & cozy gas fireplace, making it an ideal spot for gatherings and relaxation. The finished lower level offers a versatile bonus space, ideal for a second living area, entertainment space, or home office! The newly fenced-in backyard provides privacy and security. With modern comforts, a fantastic location, and a spacious, welcoming layout, this colonial-style gem is ready to become your forever home. Home warranty incl for Buyer's peace of mind!
